---
import logo1 from '../../assets/images/IntegralAsphalt/14.svg';
import logo2 from '../../assets/images/IntegralAsphalt/15.svg';
import logo3 from '../../assets/images/IntegralAsphalt/16.svg';
import logo4 from '../../assets/images/IntegralAsphalt/17.svg';
import logo5 from '../../assets/images/IntegralAsphalt/18.svg';
import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro';
---
<div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 mt-10 font-bold">
    <div class="bg-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-md p-4 mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl text-center mt-4 mb-8">Everything you need in a single unit.</h1>
        <p class="text-[#14427c] text-xl mb-5">Go directly to the job site — no need for a lowboy or flatbed, eliminating costly transport.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-start gap-4 md:gap-10">
            <div class="bg-bgMain rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center relative overflow-hidden min-h-[350px]">
                <Image src={logo1} alt="" class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-contain z-0"/>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-lg border-b-2 border-b-blueMain pb-4 mb-4 text-grisT">Perfect for small projects, patching, and premixed seals.</h1>
                    <p class="font-normal text-grisT text-justify">
                        Perfect for small-scale jobs such as patching, resurfacing, and premixed seals. Its compact design and 
                        efficient operation make
                         it ideal for quick, cost-effective hot-mix production on demand.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-bgMain rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center relative overflow-hidden min-h-[350px]">
                <Image src={logo2} alt="" class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-contain z-0"/>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-lg border-b-2 border-b-redBg pb-4 mb-4 text-grisT">
                    Produce your asphalt mix directly at the paving site</h1>
                <p class="font-normal text-grisT text-justify">
                    Produce your hot-mix directly at the paving site, eliminating the need for transport from external plants.
                     This speeds up work, reduces costs, and ensures the mix is always fresh and at the right temperature.
                </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-bgMain rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center relative overflow-hidden min-h-[350px]">
                <Image src={logo3} alt="" class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-contain z-0"/>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-lg border-b-2 border-b-redBg pb-4 mb-4 text-grisT">
                    Zero emissions, ready to work in any city.</h1>
                <p class="font-normal text-grisT text-justify">
                    The 10 TPH Integral Asphalt Plant is a low-emission, eco-friendly solution for urban projects.
                     With advanced technology and efficient design, it meets strict environmental standards while delivering 
                     high performance.</p>
                    </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-bgMain rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center min-h-[350px]">
                <Image src={logo4} alt="" class="w-1/2"/>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                <h1 class="text-grisT lg:text-2xl text-lg">Continuous production <br> for 10 hours</h1>
                <p class="font-normal text-grisT lg:text-lg text-base">with full tank
                </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-bgMain rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center relative overflow-hidden min-h-[350px]">
                <Image src={logo5} alt="" class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-contain z-0"/>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-lg border-b-2 border-b-blueMain pb-4 mb-4 text-grisT">
                    Free yourself from local mix suppliers for small jobs.</h1>
                <p class="font-normal text-grisT text-justify">
                    With the 10 TPH Integral Asphalt Plant, you can eliminate the reliance on local mix suppliers for small projects.
                     This self-sufficient solution allows for complete control over your hot-mix production, reducing costs and 
                     ensuring high-quality results on demand.
                </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-bgMain rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center min-h-[350px]">
                <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-lg text-grisT">
                    Drum Mixer Flights</h1>
                <p class="border-b-2 border-b-redBg pb-4 mb-4 font-normal text-grisT">Conventional flights, as in any standard-capacity drum mixer</p>
                <ul class="text-blueMain font-normal text-start w-full list-disc pl-8">
                    <li>Inlet Flights</li>
                    <li>Drying Veiling Flights</li>
                    <li>Radiation Flights</li>
                    <li>Heating Flights</li>
                    <li>Mixing Flights</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bgMain px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl md:rounded-full border border-blueMain mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-center lg:text-lg text-base">Reduces production costs for small-volume asphalt manufacturing by 
                optimizing startups, minimizing fuel consumption, and lowering labor and 
                transportation expenses.</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-lg lg:text-2xl text-grisT mb-6">Minimal Installation, Maximum Autonomy</h1>
    <p class="font-normal text-grisT text-base lg:text-lg">The Triaso® 10 TPH Integral Asphalt Plant is engineered for rapid deployment and independent operation. 
        Thanks to its pre-installed components, self-contained systems, and factory-set configurations,
         it requires minimal on-site setup—just position, connect fuel and power, and start producing.
          Ideal for remote or temporary jobsites, this unit eliminates the need for external infrastructure, 
          enabling fully autonomous asphalt production anywhere it's needed.
        </p>
</div>